value.0: This grotesquely disfigured creature seems to be in a permanent state of pain. It's ratlike body is twisted and almost human.
The slick stone is warm to the touch as it winds upwards toward the Barrow Site above. You can hear the gurgling water churning within it. The Cavanaugh Stone is near.
Dim light shines down from a well-hole far above. The rope looks sturdy enough to hold your weight should you need it to.
Place this object in any area where you want tracking to occur.  Set Will to the DC of tracking in this area.
